App-ZofCMS-Plugin-UserLogin

The module is a plugin for L<App::ZofCMS>; it provides functionality to
restrict access to some pages based on user accounts
(which support "roles")

Plugin uses HTTP cookies to set user sessions.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc App::ZofCMS::Plugin::UserLogin

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=App-ZofCMS-Plugin-UserLogin

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/App-ZofCMS-Plugin-UserLogin

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/App-ZofCMS-Plugin-UserLogin

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/App-ZofCMS-Plugin-UserLogin


